.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_killer -  This method checks if the player is a guard killer
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_killer(string place_name,
mixed player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^place_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the place to check if the
player is a killer in
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the name or object of the player to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if they're a guard killer, 0 if not

.EI

